Did you consider using https://www.pantsbuild.org/docs/reference-shunit2_tests here? I think this might simplify the behaviour when adding more tests: just add another `..._test.sh` file (and any requisite dependency overrides), and it'll do the right thing, rather than needing to duplicate this content. E.g.

```python
shunit2_tests(
    dependencies=["//build-support/bin/act:act-at-root"],
    overrides={
       "auto_cherry_picker_test.sh": dict(dependencies=[".github/workflows/auto-cherry-picker.yaml"]),
    },
)
